Create a jsconfig.json file (if you don’t have tsconfig.json)

Since your project is React + Vite + JavaScript, you need jsconfig.json.

Create this file at root of your frontend:

jsconfig.json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "baseUrl": ".",
    "paths": {
      "@/*": ["src/*"]
    }
  }
}


If you already have tsconfig.json, then add the same "paths" there.

✅ 2. Restart the terminal (important for Vite to pick up aliases)

Close the terminal → open again → run:

npx shadcn@latest init